245	// NewResolver constructs the dnsresolve.Resolver implementation the
246	// (validated) [dns] block selects: dnsresolve.NewSystemResolver for the
247	// default/system mode, dnsresolve.NewDoHResolver/NewDoTResolver for doh/dot,
248	// or their *WithBootstrap variants when bootstrap_ip is set. Callers
249	// normally obtain a DNS value via config.Load, which already ran
